query:
INSERT INTO jobs (
            id, name, payload, priority, status,
            run_at, attempts, max_attempts, idempotency_key
        ) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, 0, 5, $7)
        ON CONFLICT (idempotency_key) DO UPDATE
            SET status = EXCLUDED.status,
                run_at = EXCLUDED.run_at
        RETURNING id
